Template variables:

IOCTOP   - The ioc/common directory for this IOC.
TOP      - The ioc/xxx directory for this IOC, where xxx is the three-letter hutch.
ENGINEER - The engineer responsible for this IOC.
LOCATION - The location of this IOC.

Template instances:

LAKESHORE:
    NAME        - The base PV name for this variable leak valve VAT590.
    PORT        - The terminal server:port connected to this variab:le leak valve VAT590.
    ASYNTRACE   - This should be set to turn on asyn tracing for this variable leak valve VAT590.
    DATASCAN    - The rate at which the IOC scans data fields such as temperatures. Default is every 1 second.
    CONFSCAN    - The rate at which the IOC scans configuration fields. Default is every 5 seconds.
